bodyContent.introFirstLine: Welcome to Fetarute！A vanilla Minecraft server featuring City Constructions and Transportation。
bodyContent.introSecondLine: Established in 2017, and looking for being better!
bodyContent.introFirstLineCreative: The Creating is the tradition playing pattern in Fetarute. We expecting the cities made up by blocks express the community-driven creativity and illustrate the future ideas.
bodyContent.introSecondLineCreative: We warmly welcome any artists! No matter what you are good at, here's always place for you.
